  "description": {
    "zh": "气色不错啊，大兵。看样子你还待在这破地儿没走？闲话不多说了。我这有件事儿，挺敏感的事情。我们现在算是互相信任了吧？所以现在我也信任你。我不能告诉你这任务的细节信息，反正和我交给你的事没啥大关系。你的任务就是去拿一样东西，再把它放到另一个地方。听起来不难吧，但是这里有点细节问题，东西在海关，你要把它放到工厂里的某个地方。有兴趣吗？",
    "en": "Stay well, fighter. Still in our sinful world, I see? But enough of that. There is this one thing. Rather sensitive, so to say. We kind of reached mutual trust with you, right? So I’ll be trusting you with a serious task now. I won’t go into details of why, who and for what, it's not really related to the task anyway. And the task is to procure a package and move it to another place. Doesn’t sound hard, but there is a nuance. The pickup is on Customs, and the drop-off is in the Factory. Customs has a big warehouse, the red one, near the garages. The package is located there on the second floor in the office. Grab it and stash it on Factory, in a metal shack on the second floor, near the dressing room area. Interested?"
  },
